'''無段自排變速箱'''（{{lang-en|Continuously Variable Transmission}}，[[縮寫|縮寫]]：{{lang|en|'''CVT'''}}）是可以連續調節轉速／扭矩轉換比的[[自动变速器|自动变速器]]，於1879年由{{le|米爾頓·里夫斯|Milton Reeves}}發明，最初用於鋸木機器中，及後才安裝於自己的汽車之上<ref>{{cite web |title=A tale of two brothers |url=https://www.gasenginemagazine.com/gas-engines/a-tale-of-two-brothers |website=gasenginemagazine.com |access-date=19 July 2020 |language=en |archive-date=2021-11-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20211104001050/https://www.gasenginemagazine.com/gas-engines/a-tale-of-two-brothers/ |dead-url=no }}</ref>。

==簡介==
